text: Yvan Richard (born 11 December 1950) is a French ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
